  <title>Twitter compra empresa especializada em SMS</title>
  <description />
  <content>&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 11.5pt" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #666666; border-width: 1pt; border-color: windowtext; border-style: none; padding: 0cm"&gt;O Twitter anunciou hoje a compra da empresa especializada em comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o m&amp;oacute;velCloudhopper. Em mensagem no&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #666666"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #666666; border-width: 1pt; border-color: windowtext; border-style: none; padding: 0cm"&gt;&lt;a href="http://blog.twitter.com/2010/04/cloudhopping.html" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #00cbf0; border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-style: none"&gt;&lt;span style="border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-style: none"&gt;blog oficial&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, o Twitter afirma queusar&amp;aacute; a tecnologia da empresa adquirida para ampliar seus recursos de SMS emelhorar a integra&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o com operadoras de telefonia de todo o mundo desde queesteja ligada a internet.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 11.5pt" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="/blog/image.axd?picture=1.jpg" alt="" /&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="452" class="MsoNormalTable" style="width: 339.05pt; border-width: 1px !important; border-color: #bbbbbb !important; border-style: dashed !important"&gt;	&lt;tbody&gt;		&lt;tr&gt;			&lt;td style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; border-width: 1px !important; border-color: #bbbbbb !important; border-style: dashed !important; padding: 0cm"&gt;																								&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"&gt;			&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10px"&gt;Evan	 Williams: um dos fundadores do Twitter&lt;/span&gt;																								&lt;/p&gt;			&lt;/td&gt;																&lt;/tr&gt;	&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 5.75pt; line-height: 11.5pt" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #666666; border-width: 1pt; border-color: windowtext; border-style: none; padding: 0cm"&gt;O limite de 140caracteres nas mensagens do Twitter foi pensado especificamente para facilitaro uso das mensagens em celulares. O site anunciou que seus sistemas lidam comaproximadamente um bilh&amp;atilde;o de SMS mensalmente.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 5.75pt; line-height: 11.5pt" class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #666666; border-width: 1pt; border-color: windowtext; border-style: none; padding: 0cm"&gt;&amp;ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="apple-style-span"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white"&gt;Para nos ajudar a crescer e nossa escala deservi&amp;ccedil;o SMS, estamos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="apple-converted-space"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class="apple-style-span"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;o prazer de anunciar a aquisi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;ode Cloudhopper, um&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="apple-converted-space"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class="apple-style-span"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;empresa de infra-estrutura demensagens que permite ao Twitter&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="apple-converted-space"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span class="apple-style-span"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;conectar diretamente a redes deoperadoras m&amp;oacute;veis em pa&amp;iacute;ses&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="apple-converted-space"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="apple-style-span"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black"&gt;&lt;span&gt;em todo o planeta.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="apple-converted-space"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="apple-style-span"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white"&gt;Por favor, juntar-nos para acolher tanto Joe&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="apple-converted-space"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="line-height: 15px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 7.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white"&gt;&lt;span&gt;e Kristin a equipe m&amp;oacute;vel doTwitter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="apple-converted-space"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white"&gt;&amp;rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="/blog/image.axd?picture=2.png" alt="Twitter" width="396" height="255" /&gt;</content>
